10月18日，公開《Noir》的預告海報「WHO IS X?」，預告B.A.P即將回歸。10月21日，正規二輯《Noir》行程表公開<ref>{{cite news|title=11月依然是歌謠大戰　B.A.P將攜正規二輯回歸|url=http://www.nownews.com/n/2016/10/21/2278994|accessdate=2016-10-21|agency=今日新聞|date=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022023039/http://www.nownews.com/n/2016/10/21/2278994|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月25日，[[TS娛樂|TS娛樂]]表示[[方容國|方容國]]因診斷出患有[[恐慌症|恐慌症]]，將不參與《Noir》的宣傳活動<ref>{{cite web | title=B.A.P 發售新專輯關聯公布 | publisher=TS Entertainment | date=2016-10-25 | url=https://www.facebook.com/OFFICIALB.A.P/posts/1154158248003003 | language=zh | accessdate=2016-10-25 | archive-date=2019-02-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215135830/https://www.facebook.com/OFFICIALB.A.P/posts/1154158248003003 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bang Yong Guk to take hiatus due to anxiety disorder + B.A.P to promote as 5|url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2016/10/bang-yong-guk-to-take-hiatus-due-to-anxiety-disorder-bap-to-promote-as-5|accessdate=2016-10-25|agency=allkpop|date=2016-10-25|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025175240/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2016/10/bang-yong-guk-to-take-hiatus-due-to-anxiety-disorder-bap-to-promote-as-5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，[[方容國|方容國]]透過個人Twitter，向BABY們傳達歉意：「無法和成員及粉絲們一起，身為隊長只有感到可惜與抱歉」、「為了以健康的樣子回來，會盡最大的努力」，並希望BABY們多多給予成員們關心和應援。隨後，成員們也透過個人Twitter，表示會陪伴[[方容國|方容國]]、成為他的力量，並努力填滿舞台上的空缺<ref>{{cite press release | title=B.A.P Members Write Moving Tweets To Fans Following News Of Bang Yong Guk's Hiatus | publisher=soompi | date=2016-10-25 | url=http://www.soompi.com/2016/10/25/bap-members-write-moving-tweets-fans-following-news-bang-yong-guks-hiatus/ | language=en | access-date=2016-10-27 | archive-date=2016-10-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027151405/http://www.soompi.com/2016/10/25/bap-members-write-moving-tweets-fans-following-news-bang-yong-guks-hiatus/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。當晚，[[方容國|方容國]]的雙胞胎哥哥透過個人Instagram，透露：「[[方容國|方容國]]從開始歌手生涯、及持續從事音樂活動中患上[[憂鬱症|憂鬱症]]，自今年起因併發[[恐慌症|恐慌症]]而變得十分辛苦」，並提到：「會為11月7日以正規專輯回歸的另一個家族B.A.P成員們應援」，文末更以「Everything's gonna be alright」作結<ref>{{cite press release | title=Bang Yong Guk's twin brother comments on his hiatus from B.A.P | publisher=Allkpop | date=2016-10-26 | url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2016/10/bang-yong-guks-twin-brother-comments-on-his-hiatus-from-bap | language=en | access-date=2016-10-27 | archive-date=2016-10-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027122957/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2016/10/bang-yong-guks-twin-brother-comments-on-his-hiatus-from-bap | dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月26日，[[King_Records|King Records]]表示[[方容國|方容國]]已完成日語單曲六輯《Fly High》的錄音和拍攝，但以恢復健康為優先，將不參與日本的宣傳活動<ref>{{cite web | title=B.A.Pに関するお知らせ | publisher=King Records | date=2016-10-26 | url=http://www.kingrecords.co.jp/cs/t/t9061/ | language=ja | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026163330/http://www.kingrecords.co.jp/cs/t/t9061/ | archivedate=2016-10-26 | accessdate=2016-10-26 }}</ref>。

