ite web | title=[한양대 팬사인회] 멤버 불참 안내 | publisher=TS Entertainment | date=2017-04-01 | url=https://twitter.com/BAP_Fanstaff/status/848006507794800642 | language=ko | accessdate=2017-04-03 | archive-date=2017-04-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422014917/https://twitter.com/BAP_Fanstaff/status/848006507794800642 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=[잠실 팬사인회와 라디오 스케쥴] 멤버 불참 안내 | publisher=TS Entertainment | date=2017-04-02 | url=https://twitter.com/BAP_Fanstaff/status/848381323349708800 | language=ko | accessdate=2017-04-03 | archive-date=2017-04-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422021007/https://twitter.com/BAP_Fanstaff/status/848381323349708800 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

